[{"Id": "1", "ActionId": "1", "Type": "101", "BeginAnim": "AniZhuanchangEnd", "Params[1]": "Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory91.png"}, {"Id": "2", "ActionId": "2", "Type": "401", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "112"}, {"Id": "3", "ActionId": "3", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500086", "Params[4]": "400"}, {"Id": "4", "ActionId": "4", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "2", "Params[2]": "500019", "Params[4]": "-400"}, {"Id": "5", "ActionId": "5", "Type": "301", "BeginAnim": "DialogEnable", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Construct", "Params[3]": "Good thing we rendezvoused in time. Quickly, escort the civilians to the safe zone. Everyone else, keep an eye on the bionics!", "Params[4]": "2"}, {"Id": "6", "ActionId": "6", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Fisher", "Params[3]": "Err' damn cannonslinger, get your asses over 'ere!", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "7", "ActionId": "7", "Type": "301", "Params[3]": "The base is in turmoil. One group of humans is engaging with the bionics approaching the base, while another is hastily preparing for the next wave of attacks."}, {"Id": "8", "ActionId": "1001", "Type": "202", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "2"}, {"Id": "9", "ActionId": "1002", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500201", "Params[3]": "10"}, {"Id": "10", "ActionId": "8", "Type": "301", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Simon", "Params[3]": "...Ugh, I'm sorry. I don't feel so...", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "11", "ActionId": "9", "Type": "301", "Params[3]": "Simon, neither a Construct nor piloting a Polar Soldier, had no choice but to hitch a ride on Diana."}, {"Id": "12", "ActionId": "10", "Type": "301", "Params[3]": "Upon reaching the base, Simon could no longer hold his grip and tumbles off of Diana, rolling onto the ground."}, {"Id": "13", "ActionId": "1003", "Type": "302", "Params[2]": "Are you okay?", "Params[3]": "11", "Params[4]": "Didn't you go through training in Babylonia?", "Params[5]": "12"}, {"Id": "14", "ActionId": "11", "NextActionId": "3000", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Simon", "Params[3]": "Phew... I-I just need a quick breather...", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "15", "ActionId": "12", "NextActionId": "3000", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Simon", "Params[3]": "Argh... My physical training grades were just average... Ngh...", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "16", "ActionId": "3000", "Type": "202", "Params[1]": "1"}, {"Id": "17", "ActionId": "13", "Type": "301", "Params[3]": "Before he could finish, he signals for a open path and scurries behind the shade. By the look of things, he is likely going to be out of action for some time."}, {"Id": "18", "ActionId": "1004", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500206", "Params[3]": "1"}, {"Id": "19", "ActionId": "14", "Type": "301", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Atiel", "Params[3]": "Simon's always like this. I'll go look after him.", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "20", "ActionId": "1005", "Type": "401", "Params[1]": "2", "Params[2]": "1514"}, {"Id": "21", "ActionId": "1006", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500199", "Params[3]": "5", "Params[4]": "-400"}, {"Id": "22", "ActionId": "1007", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "2", "Params[2]": "500214", "Params[3]": "4", "Params[4]": "400"}, {"Id": "23", "ActionId": "15", "Type": "301", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Staessen", "Params[3]": "The code! Did you guys find it?!", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "24", "ActionId": "16", "Type": "301", "Params[3]": "Captain Staessen pushes his way from out of the crowd. Handing over the command to one of his subordinates, he begins to shake Atiel vigorously."}, {"Id": "25", "ActionId": "1008", "Type": "302", "Params[2]": "Calm down!", "Params[3]": "17", "Params[4]": "Derek's voice is the code.", "Params[5]": "19"}, {"Id": "26", "ActionId": "17", "NextActionId": "18", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Staessen", "Params[3]": "How can I calm down at a time like this? Do you know how dire the situation is? What on earth is the code to control Amberia?!", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "27", "ActionId": "18", "NextActionId": "20", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Rosetta", "Params[3]": "It's Derek. More specifically, it's his voice.", "Params[4]": "2"}, {"Id": "28", "ActionId": "19", "NextActionId": "20", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Staessen", "Params[3]": "Derek... You mean that mechanic narwhal?!", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "29", "ActionId": "20", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Staessen", "Params[3]": "Wait... Why is that mechanical narwhal's voice the code? They're using a voice to control Amberia?", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "30", "ActionId": "21", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Rosetta", "Params[3]": "I can't tell what they were thinking either, but I'm afraid it's true. Derek's voice is specifically designed to resonate with the frequency of humanoid-hybrid M.I.N.D.s.", "Params[4]": "2"}, {"Id": "31", "ActionId": "22", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Staessen", "Params[3]": "How is that possible?", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "32", "ActionId": "23", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Rosetta", "Params[3]": "You must know what I mean, Commandant. You saw it firsthand.", "Params[4]": "2"}, {"Id": "33", "ActionId": "1009", "Type": "302", "Params[2]": "Our last time in the ARU..."}, {"Id": "34", "ActionId": "24", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Rosetta", "Params[3]": "Yeah. Derek's voice was the main reason I wasn't taken by the virus. I didn't realize at the time, but looking back, Derek may be the key to everything.", "Params[4]": "2"}, {"Id": "35", "ActionId": "1010", "Type": "202", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "2"}, {"Id": "36", "ActionId": "1011", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500088", "Params[3]": "4"}, {"Id": "37", "ActionId": "25", "Type": "301", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Diana", "Params[3]": "Now that you mention it, even though Derek swims all over the world, he always returns at a specific time.", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "38", "ActionId": "1012", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500199", "Params[3]": "4", "Params[4]": "-400"}, {"Id": "39", "ActionId": "1013", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "2", "Params[2]": "500214", "Params[3]": "4", "Params[4]": "400"}, {"Id": "40", "ActionId": "26", "Type": "301", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Staessen", "Params[3]": "The ebb and flow of the tide... You mean, that narwhal is the key to putting Amberia to rest?", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "41", "ActionId": "27", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Rosetta", "Params[3]": "Looks like it...", "Params[4]": "2"}, {"Id": "42", "ActionId": "1014", "Type": "302", "Params[2]": "Where is Derek now?", "Params[3]": "28", "Params[4]": "Will Derek be returning soon?", "Params[5]": "29"}, {"Id": "43", "ActionId": "28", "NextActionId": "31", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Staessen", "Params[3]": "...Who knows where that blasted narwhal is!", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "44", "ActionId": "29", "NextActionId": "30", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Rosetta", "Params[3]": "He usually shows up at about this time, so he should have. We all assumed it was part of his migration cycle, but this time, Derek is running late.", "Params[4]": "2"}, {"Id": "45", "ActionId": "30", "NextActionId": "31", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Rosetta", "Params[3]": "As a result...", "Params[4]": "2"}, {"Id": "46", "ActionId": "31", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Rosetta", "Params[3]": "Derek might be malfunctioning. The reason being...", "Params[4]": "2"}, {"Id": "47", "ActionId": "1015", "Type": "302", "Params[2]": "\u03b1", "Params[3]": "32"}, {"Id": "48", "ActionId": "32", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Rosetta", "Params[3]": "That must be it. Alpha had her eyes on Derek during her last visit, and in trying to \"tame\" him, she must have caused a system malfunction.", "Params[4]": "2"}, {"Id": "49", "ActionId": "33", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Staessen", "Params[3]": "Then what do we do? No Derek, no code...", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "50", "ActionId": "1016", "Type": "302", "Params[2]": "Evan has the code.", "Params[3]": "1017"}, {"Id": "51", "ActionId": "1017", "Type": "202", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "2"}, {"Id": "52", "ActionId": "1018", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500088", "Params[3]": "4"}, {"Id": "53", "ActionId": "34", "Type": "301", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Diana", "Params[3]": "Why Evan... Ah...", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "54", "ActionId": "35", "Type": "301", "EndAnim": "AniZhuanchangBegin", "Params[3]": "Diana suddenly recalls the last time she saw Evan."}, {"Id": "55", "ActionId": "1019", "Type": "202", "Params[1]": "1"}, {"Id": "56", "ActionId": "1020", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500198"}, {"Id": "57", "ActionId": "1021", "Type": "101", "Params[1]": "Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory217.png"}, {"Id": "58", "ActionId": "36", "Type": "301", "BeginAnim": "AniZhuanchangEnd", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Evan", "Params[3]": "Supersonic Derek Wahoo!", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "59", "ActionId": "37", "Type": "301", "EndAnim": "AniZhuanchangBegin", "Params[2]": "Player", "Params[3]": "'\u2014\u2014'", "Params[6]": "1"}, {"Id": "60", "ActionId": "1022", "Type": "101", "Params[1]": "Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory91.png"}, {"Id": "61", "ActionId": "1023", "Type": "202", "Params[1]": "1"}, {"Id": "62", "ActionId": "1024", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500088", "Params[3]": "4"}, {"Id": "63", "ActionId": "38", "Type": "301", "BeginAnim": "AniZhuanchangEnd", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Diana", "Params[3]": "That's definitely Derek's voice.. Wait, where's Evan?", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "64", "ActionId": "1025", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500198", "Params[3]": "14", "Params[4]": "400"}, {"Id": "65", "ActionId": "39", "Type": "301", "BeginAnim": "PanelActor1Shake", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Evan", "Params[3]": "Wah!", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "66", "ActionId": "1026", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500206", "Params[3]": "2"}, {"Id": "67", "ActionId": "40", "Type": "301", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[3]": "Before you could react, Evan has already fallen to the ground. A familiar female Construct has snatched the voice player around his neck, radiating a terrifying smile on her face."}, {"Id": "68", "ActionId": "1027", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500088", "Params[3]": "4"}, {"Id": "69", "ActionId": "41", "Type": "301", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Diana", "Params[3]": "A-Atiel?!", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "70", "ActionId": "1028", "Type": "302", "Params[2]": "(Shoot grapple at her)", "Params[3]": "4000", "Params[4]": "(Charge at her)", "Params[5]": "5000"}, {"Id": "71", "ActionId": "4000", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500206", "Params[3]": "2"}, {"Id": "72", "ActionId": "42", "Type": "301", "Params[3]": "You pilot the Polar Soldier to attack Atiel."}, {"Id": "73", "ActionId": "43", "Type": "301", "BeginAnim": "PanelActor1Shake", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Atiel", "Params[3]": "\u2014\u2014!", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "74", "ActionId": "4002", "Type": "401", "Params[1]": "2", "Params[2]": "10004001"}, {"Id": "75", "ActionId": "44", "Type": "301", "Params[3]": "The grappling hook scratches Atiel's torso, causing vitual fluid to spray out."}, {"Id": "76", "ActionId": "45", "NextActionId": "5003", "Type": "301", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Atiel", "Params[3]": "Ugh... Dammit!", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "77", "ActionId": "5000", "NextActionId": "46", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500206", "Params[3]": "2"}, {"Id": "78", "ActionId": "46", "NextActionId": "47", "Type": "301", "Params[3]": "You pilot the Polar Soldier to attack Atiel."}, {"Id": "79", "ActionId": "47", "NextActionId": "48", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Atiel", "Params[3]": "Boss, you're way off mark.", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "80", "ActionId": "48", "NextActionId": "49", "Type": "301", "Params[3]": "Atiel dodges your charge, but Rosetta quickly follows with a throw of her spear."}, {"Id": "81", "ActionId": "49", "NextActionId": "50", "Type": "301", "BeginAnim": "PanelActor1Shake", "Params[2]": "Atiel", "Params[3]": "What?!", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "82", "ActionId": "50", "NextActionId": "5002", "Type": "301", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[3]": "The spear strikes Atiel, causing vital fluid to spray out."}, {"Id": "83", "ActionId": "5002", "NextActionId": "51", "Type": "401", "Params[1]": "2", "Params[2]": "10004001"}, {"Id": "84", "ActionId": "51", "NextActionId": "5003", "Type": "301", "Params[2]": "Atiel", "Params[3]": "Cough... Dammit!", "Params[4]": "1"}, {"Id": "85", "ActionId": "5003", "Type": "202", "Params[1]": "1"}, {"Id": "86", "ActionId": "52", "Type": "301", "Params[3]": "The terrain, however, makes the attack ineffectual, giving Atiel an opportunity to escape and run the other way."}, {"Id": "87", "ActionId": "53", "Type": "301", "Params[3]": "Rosetta activates her light wings and flies into the air."}, {"Id": "88", "ActionId": "1029", "Type": "201", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "500214", "Params[3]": "5"}, {"Id": "89", "ActionId": "54", "Type": "301", "IsEnd": "1", "EndAnim": "AniZhuanchangBegin", "Params[1]": "1", "Params[2]": "Rosetta", "Params[3]": "Catch her, Commandant!", "Params[4]": "1"}]